name: Forest Spirit
description:
Among my friends there are extraordinary people, those who live in full force, burn like a big fire and attract others to their projects and deeds.
These are the people of the Giants, the Heroes of our time.
One of such people is Eduard Yasaveev, a forest spirit, a conductor of sound and the creator of @Dzin.Space
A flaming bonfire that rushes forward and upward.

I dedicate this sculpture to him, with gratitude and respect for everything he does.
And with this work I start a new series of sculptures, which will be called "Neo Heroes", in which I will add the same shining people like Ed.
Neo Heroes series. 2021
